          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[#8B5CF6]">E-Commerce</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold mt-1">대규모 이커머스 플랫폼</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/30 mt-1">일 100만 트래픽 처리 가능한 마이크로서비스 아키텍처.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group reveal" style="--delay: 2;">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/5">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512941937669-90a1b58e7e9c?q=80&w=800" alt="모바일 앱" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-700 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[#8B5CF6]">Mobile App</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold mt-1">핀테크 모바일 앱</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/30 mt-1">Flutter 기반 크로스플랫폼 금융 서비스 앱 개발.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== 기술스택 ========== -->
  <section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <span class="text-sm font-mono font-semibold text-[#8B5CF6] tracking-wider uppercase reveal" style="--delay: 0;">Tech Stack</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mt-4 reveal" style="--delay: 1;">우리의 기술력</h2>
          </div>

          <p class="text-white/30 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed reveal" style="--delay: 2;">
            최신 기술 스택과 업계 최고의 엔지니어가 함께합니다. 10년 이상의 경험으로 검증된 기술력을 보유하고 있습니다.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 reveal" style="--delay: 3;">
            <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
              <p class="font-mono font-bold text-[#8B5CF6] text-sm">Frontend</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">React, Next.js, Vue, Svelte</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
              <p class="font-mono font-bold text-[#8B5CF6] text-sm">Backend</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">Node, Python, Go, Rust</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
              <p class="font-mono font-bold text-[#8B5CF6] text-sm">Cloud</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">AWS, GCP, Azure, K8s</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
              <p class="font-mono font-bold text-[#8B5CF6] text-sm">AI / ML</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">PyTorch, TensorFlow, LLM</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative hidden lg:block reveal" style="--delay: 0;">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?q=80&w=800" alt="개발" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl border border-white/5 opacity-70" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== 문의 ========== -->
