              <li><a href="#services" class="text-white/30 text-sm hover:text-[#8B5CF6] transition font-mono">AI / ML</a></li>
              <li><a href="#services" class="text-white/30 text-sm hover:text-[#8B5CF6] transition font-mono">Cloud</a></li>
              <li><a href="#services" class="text-white/30 text-sm hover:text-[#8B5CF6] transition font-mono">Web / App</a></li>
              <li><a href="#services" class="text-white/30 text-sm hover:text-[#8B5CF6] transition font-mono">Security</a></li>
